Title: Pion in a Box
Authors: W. Bietenholz and M. GÃ¶ckeler and R. Horsley and Y. Nakamura and D. Pleiter and P. E. L. Rakow and G. Schierholz and J. M. Zanotti
Abstract: The residual mass of the pion in a finite spatial box at vanishing quark masses, the mass gap, is computed with two flavors of dynamical clover fermions. The result is compared with predictions of chiral perturbation theory in the delta regime.
